item.title: 1.16 Packs
item.description: Note This section might not always be up-to-date. Please let us know or submit changes if you discover this is the case. To find out how see contributing. 1.16 vs 1.12 Packs Many of you are already familiar with 1.12.2 and 1.16 packs but there are some key changes that seemingly impact all 1.16 packs as a whole. As a result of this you’re likely wondering what’s changed and how you can work around it.
